      ``` csharp
      var smartSqlMapper = serviceProvider.GetSmartSqlMapper("SmartSql");
      var smartSqlMapper_1 = serviceProvider.GetSmartSqlMapper("SmartSql-1");
      ```
      ]]>
    </PackageReleaseNotes>
    <PackageTags>orm sql read-write-separation cache  redis dotnet-core cross-platform high-performance distributed-computing zookeeper</PackageTags>
